95
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:56,060
The reason for divorce is
domestic violence by Zhang Yuan.

96
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,680
On April 17,

97
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,750
Zhang Yuan left work early

98
00:05:58,750 --> 00:06:00,430
and bought a boning knife,

99
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:02,390
