as a murder weapon.

100
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:04,990
He arrived at Jiang Ting's place
after dinner.

101
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,160
The quick wash mode
of this washing machine

102
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,070
